<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Entrepreneur Community - HarmonyHub</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/CSS/business-community.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/CSS/header.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/CSS/body.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/CSS/fonts.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/CSS/fixed-footer.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/CSS/footer.css">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Matemasie&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Nerko+One&family=Sevillana&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
</head>
<body>

    <!-- Header Section (Reused from the main page) -->
    {{>header}}

    <section class="hero-section">
        <div class="container">
            <h1>{{name}}</h1>
            <p>{{description}}</p>
            <a href="/signup" class="btn hero-btn">Get Started</a>
        </div>
    </section>
    
    <section class="success-stories-section">
        <div class="container">
            <h2>Startup Success Stories</h2>
            <div class="stories-grid">
                <div class="story-item">
                    <img src="/src/Images/user3.webp" alt="Startup Success 1">
                    <h4>Rohit Nandha - Tech Innovator</h4>
                    <p>From a small idea to a thriving tech company, Rohit's journey is a testament to the power of perseverance.</p>
                    <a href="/signup" class="btn">Read More</a>
                </div>
                <div class="story-item">
                    <img src="/src/Images/user5.webp" alt="Startup Success 2">
                    <h4>Vrushabh Patel - E-commerce Pioneer</h4>
                    <p>Learn how Vrushabh built a leading e-commerce platform from scratch, disrupting the industry.</p>
                    <a href="/signup" class="btn">Read More</a>
                </div>
                <div class="story-item">
                    <img src="/src/Images/user6.webp" alt="Startup Success 3">
                    <h4>Anjali Lakhani - Social Entrepreneur</h4>
                    <p>Anjali's mission-driven approach has not only brought her success but also created a positive social impact.</p>
                    <a href="/signup" class="btn">Read More</a>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>
    
    <section class="resources-section">
        <div class="container">
            <h2>Essential Resources and Tools</h2>
            <div class="filters">
                <select id="phase-filter">
                    <option value="all">All Phases</option>
                    <option value="startup">Startup</option>
                    <option value="growth">Growth</option>
                    <option value="scaling">Scaling</option>
                </select>
                <select id="industry-filter">
                    <option value="all">All Industries</option>
                    <option value="tech">Tech</option>
                    <option value="ecommerce">E-commerce</option>
                    <option value="services">Services</option>
                </select>
                <select id="tool-filter">
                    <option value="all">All Tools</option>
                    <option value="business-plan">Business Plan</option>
                    <option value="funding">Funding</option>
                    <option value="marketing">Marketing</option>
                </select>
            </div>
            <div class="resources-grid">
                <div class="resource-item" data-phase="startup" data-industry="tech" data-tool="business-plan">
                    <h4>Business Plan Template</h4>
                    <p>Get started with this comprehensive business plan template tailored for tech startups.</p>
                    <a href="/signup" class="btn">Download</a>
                </div>
                <div class="resource-item" data-phase="growth" data-industry="ecommerce" data-tool="funding">
                    <h4>Funding Guide for E-commerce</h4>
                    <p>Learn how to secure funding to take your e-commerce business to the next level.</p>
                    <a href="/signup" class="btn">Read More</a>
                </div>
                <div class="resource-item" data-phase="scaling" data-industry="services" data-tool="marketing">
                    <h4>Marketing Strategies for Service Businesses</h4>
                    <p>Explore proven marketing strategies that will help scale your service-based business.</p>
                    <a href="/signup" class="btn">Explore</a>
                </div>
                <!-- Add more resource items as needed -->
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>
    
    <section class="mentorship-section">
        <div class="container">
            <h2>Mentorship and Networking</h2>
            <div class="mentorship-grid">
                <div class="mentor-item">
                    <img src="/src/business/sarah-lee.webp" alt="Mentor 1">
                    <h4>Sarah Lee</h4>
                    <p>Expert in Tech Startups</p>
                    <a href="/signup" class="btn">Book a Session</a>
                </div>
                <div class="mentor-item">
                    <img src="/src/business/david-chen.webp" alt="Mentor 2">
                    <h4>David Chen</h4>
                    <p>Marketing Guru</p>
                    <a href="/signup" class="btn">Book a Session</a>
                </div>
                <div class="mentor-item">
                    <img src="/src/business/linda-adams.webp" alt="Mentor 3">
                    <h4>Linda Adams</h4>
                    <p>Funding and Investment Expert</p>
                    <a href="/signup" class="btn">Book a Session</a>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="networking-events">
                <h3>Upcoming Networking Events</h3>
                <div class="event-item">
                    <h4>Virtual Networking for Tech Entrepreneurs</h4>
                    <p>Join us for an evening of networking with tech industry leaders and fellow entrepreneurs.</p>
                    <a href="/signup" class="btn">Join Now</a>
                </div>
                <div class="event-item">
                    <h4>Pitch Night</h4>
                    <p>Present your startup to a panel of investors and get valuable feedback.</p>
                    <a href="/signup" class="btn">Register</a>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>
    
    <section class="workshops-section">
        <div class="container">
            <h2>Upcoming Workshops and Webinars</h2>
            <div class="workshops-grid">
                <div class="workshop-item">
                    <h4>Building a Scalable Business Model</h4>
                    <p>Learn from industry experts how to create a business model that scales.</p>
                    <a href="/signup" class="btn">Sign Up</a>
                </div>
                <div class="workshop-item">
                    <h4>Digital Marketing Strategies for Startups</h4>
                    <p>Explore the latest digital marketing strategies to grow your startup.</p>
                    <a href="/signup" class="btn">Register</a>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>
    
    <section class="signup-cta-section">
        <div class="container">
            <p>Join our entrepreneur community and take your business to the next level. <a href="/signup" class="btn">Sign up now</a> to explore more!</p>
        </div>
    </section>
    
    
    

    <!--fixed footer part-->
    <div class="fixed-footer">
        <p>Join HarmonyHub to explore more...! <a href="/signup" class="btn">Join Now</a> | <a href="/login" class="btn">Login</a></p>
    </div>

    <!--footer part-->
    {{>footer}}
</body>
</html>
